Package: OrangeR
Title: A Purpose-Driven ETL Pipeline for Ensuring Fairness and Accuracy in Timesheet Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Gray", email = "james.gray@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID", work_id = "JG3288"))
Description: A purpose-driven ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) toolkit committed to transforming messy, error-prone timesheet data into a source of truth. By systematically ingesting, cleaning, and validating data from diverse sources like unstructured PDFs and CSVs, this package ensures the accuracy and fairness of payroll and compliance systems. Its core mission is to empower institutions by providing a transparent, auditable, and robust data foundation, thereby fostering trust and enabling meaningful, data-informed action.
